---

<section class="bg-[#F8FAFC] py-8 px-6 sm:py-14">
    <div class="max-w-screen-xl mx-auto bg-dark-700 rounded-2xl px-8 py-10 sm:px-14 sm:py-12 relative overflow-hidden">
      <!-- Subtle radial glow -->
      <div class="absolute inset-0 pointer-events-none" style="background: radial-gradient(ellipse 60% 50% at 80% 50%, rgba(88,139,103,0.15) 0%, transparent 70%);" aria-hidden="true"></div>

      <div class="relative z-10 flex flex-col lg:flex-row lg:items-center lg:gap-14">
        <!-- Photo -->
        <div class="flex justify-center lg:justify-start mb-8 lg:mb-0 flex-shrink-0">
          <img src="/jitan-bg.png" class="w-32 h-32 object-cover rounded-full ring-4 ring-primary-600 ring-offset-4 ring-offset-dark-700" alt="Jitan Gupta">
        </div>

        <!-- Text -->
        <div class="flex-1">
          <p class="text-primary-300 text-xs font-semibold uppercase tracking-widest mb-3">Building with AI. Teaching engineers.</p>
          <h2 class="text-2xl sm:text-3xl font-bold text-white mb-4">Follow the experiments that survive real engineering work.</h2>
          <p class="text-gray-300 leading-relaxed mb-3">I pull apart Claude Code, MCP servers, and agent frameworks to understand what actually helps engineers ship better software.</p>
          <p class="text-gray-400 text-sm leading-relaxed mb-8">The useful parts become YouTube videos, open source builds, and practical frameworks you can try in your own workflow.</p>

          <div class="flex flex-wrap gap-3">
            <a href="https://www.youtube.com/@jitangupta" target="_blank" rel="noopener noreferrer"
              class="inline-flex items-center gap-2 text-white px-5 py-2.5 rounded-lg bg-primary-600 hover:bg-primary-500 transition text-sm font-medium">
              <svg xmlns="http://www.w3.org/2000/svg" width="16" height="16" viewBox="0 0 24 24" fill="none" stroke="currentColor" stroke-width="2" stroke-linecap="round" stroke-linejoin="round"><path d="M2.5 17a24.12 24.12 0 0 1 0-10 2 2 0 0 1 1.4-1.4 49.56 49.56 0 0 1 16.2 0A2 2 0 0 1 21.5 7a24.12 24.12 0 0 1 0 10 2 2 0 0 1-1.4 1.4 49.55 49.55 0 0 1-16.2 0A2 2 0 0 1 2.5 17"/><path d="m10 15 5-3-5-3z"/></svg>
              Watch on YouTube
            </a>
            <a href="/frameworks"
              class="inline-flex items-center gap-2 text-gray-300 px-5 py-2.5 rounded-lg border border-gray-600 hover:border-primary-400 hover:text-primary-300 transition text-sm font-medium">
              <svg xmlns="http://www.w3.org/2000/svg" width="16" height="16" viewBox="0 0 24 24" fill="none" stroke="currentColor" stroke-width="2" stroke-linecap="round" stroke-linejoin="round"><path d="M8 3H5a2 2 0 0 0-2 2v3"/><path d="M16 3h3a2 2 0 0 1 2 2v3"/><path d="M8 21H5a2 2 0 0 1-2-2v-3"/><path d="M16 21h3a2 2 0 0 0 2-2v-3"/><path d="M9 9h6v6H9z"/></svg>
              See frameworks
            </a>
          </div>
        </div>
      </div>
    </div>
</section>
